#

Sautéed Garlic Shrimp with Lemon Butter Sauce

$22
600 kcal
Difficulty: 45%

Allergens:

ShellfishDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairySeafood

Tags:

SeafoodItalianComfort Food

Description

Succulent shrimp sautéed to perfection in a zesty lemon butter sauce, served over creamy parmesan risotto with vibrant roasted vegetables.

Ingredients

  • Shrimp: 1 lb
  • Garlic: 4 cloves
  • Butter: 6 tbsp
  • Lemon Juice: 2 tbsp
  • Parmesan Cheese: 1 cup
  • Arborio Rice: 1 cup
  • Vegetable Broth: 4 cups
  • Broccolini: 1 bunch
  • Cherry Tomatoes: 1 cup
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
